name: Extraction not possible from raw text alone
description: Direct extraction from raw text without access to the webpage or its schema/metadata is not feasible. For extracting owner type, data theme, and ISO 19115 theme as per your schema, you would need the actual page content or at least a sample of its HTML/metadata, not just the URL. Please provide more details, HTML code, or metadata snippet for extraction, or use a web scraping tool directly on the site.
